{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "I have enough context to sketch the implementation path: 1. Add a curated music catalog plus durable mix-policy metadata on the backend. 2. Insert a post-processing mixer after narration assembly, keeping raw TTS unchanged. 3. Expose the...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_21", "text": "I have enough context to sketch the implementation path:\n\n1. Add a curated music catalog plus durable mix-policy metadata on the backend.\n2. Insert a post-processing mixer after narration assembly, keeping raw TTS unchanged.\n3. Expose the curated track metadata to the UI so the existing audio settings form maps to real mix behavior.\n4. Add targeted backend/frontend tests, then run API/unit checks and browser validation for the audio settings UI.\n\nI\u2019m reading the session service, storage paths, and existing audio tests now so the changes align with current persistence and asset conventions.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 43, "prompt_index": 75, "prompt_name": "74 \u2014 Background Music Mixing Pipeline", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T15:26:04-07:00"}
