{"color": "green", "emoji": "\ud83d\udcac", "event_type": "Agent Message", "message": "Implemented the background-music pipeline and committed the feature work on the current branch as `35ee6f6` (`feat(prompt-74): background music mixing`). The backend now has a curated music catalog, durable `music_mix` plan generation, f...", "raw_event": {"item": {"id": "item_243", "text": "Implemented the background-music pipeline and committed the feature work on the current branch as `35ee6f6` (`feat(prompt-74): background music mixing`).\n\nThe backend now has a curated music catalog, durable `music_mix` plan generation, ffmpeg-based post-processing mixing with ducking, narration-master preservation, and richer final-asset metadata. The audio settings API/frontend now expose music profile options plus a persisted mix preview, and the audio stage UI shows backend-driven mix guidance and recommended bed levels.\n\nVerification completed:\n- Backend: targeted pytest coverage for mix planning, ffmpeg wrapper behavior, durable audio-job mixing, session saves, and API responses.\n- Frontend: `AudioSettingsStage` tests passed and `npm run build` passed.\n- Runtime: real ffmpeg smoke test inside Docker confirmed a `2.0s` source stays `2.0s` after mixing.\n- Browser QA: ran the compose browser spec and captured screenshots at `.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-74-audio-music-on.png` and `.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-74-audio-music-off.png`.\n\nThe required reviewer summary was written to [summary.md](/Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.yolopilot/runs/20260331T205548_storyteller_prompt_pack/74_background_music_mixing_pipeline/summary.md). Unrelated `.yolopilot` log/status files remain uncommitted.", "type": "agent_message"}, "type": "item.completed"}, "task_display_context": {"event_number": 488, "prompt_index": 75, "prompt_name": "74 \u2014 Background Music Mixing Pipeline", "prompt_total": 100}, "timestap": "2026-04-02T15:56:50-07:00"}
